The paper deals with the development of QoE models using machine learning, which involves multimedia (MM) processing and learning algorithms (LG). The focus is on video quality estimation, which falls under computer vision (CV) and information retrieval (IR). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of sharing sensitive data, which could be related to cybersecurity (CR). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.MM and cs.LG, followed by cs.CV, cs.IR, and cs.CR.
